@startuml 时序图
actor User
participant UI
participant AppLogic
participant Database
participant StatEngine


User -> UI: 填写账目信息并提交()
UI -> AppLogic: submitEntry(entryData)
AppLogic -> Database: saveEntry(entry)
Database --> AppLogic: saveResult(success)
AppLogic -> StatEngine: updateStatistics(entry)
StatEngine --> AppLogic: statsUpdated
AppLogic --> UI: submitResult(success)
UI -> User: 显示保存成功


@enduml